                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900707-31-off150 t17900707-31-cd151"></join>, eighteen pounds weight of lead, value 2 s. 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17900707-31-victim314" type="victimName">
                     Samuel 
                     Mayo
                  <interp inst="t17900707-31-victim314" type="surname" value="Mayo"></interp>
